Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship! Romance! Mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We try our best because we've made those promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, we have a 1-hour special!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A theme park sounds the bells of a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wedding at Huis ten Bosch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to go to Huis Ten Bosch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it really OK for you to have invited us as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't we be troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way—if I went alone, it'd be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, if something happens, you'll be there to help out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Something happens"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, there seem to have been a lot of problems prior to the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Shinya and I have been friends ever since I could walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, everyone was saying that we should get married some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though that has nothing to do with the wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just hope he's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never knew you could be so kind, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would anyone like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, would you like something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I have an oolong tea, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, but this is the last can of oolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can have it then, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You asked for it first, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, my apologies in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I get a paper cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being such an inconvenience!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:53.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Takahashi Junichi (27)\NOtaru Glass Artisan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Siblings on a vacation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're not siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why is it every time Ran goes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This four-eyed brat insists on coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without me around, no one would cook for Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what else do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I should be a little more honest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:35.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE BRIDE OF HUIS TEN BOSCH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the Shinkansen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all going to Huis ten Bosch as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going sightseeing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no need to look at me with such pity in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, how about we come along with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be able to go with such cute girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you—her escorting fee is pretty high!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Joking, joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, how much longer does she plan to keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is Huis ten Bosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his doesn't even look like it's in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, for coming to my wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing—I just happened to be taking a tour of the place is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my friend, Ran, and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri Ran, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:09.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Katori Akane (26)\NBride
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:09.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ooga Shinya (24)\NGroom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ooga Shinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my fiancee, Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Katori Akane—very pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really pretty, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot for coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gentleman is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who we met on the Shinkansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, we should get over there as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! Windmills!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's a bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, look! Swans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're so graceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're actually in the Netherlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you see why we picked this place for our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, when you get married, will you hold your wedding here at Huis ten Bosch as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still a high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, already have somewhere in mind for that special someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since when did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:24.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Europa Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, this is Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and her companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:43.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ooga Tatsuya (55)\NOoga Financial Group Head\NShioya's Father
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:43.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ooga Masayo (52)\NShinya's Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the young missis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must thank you for traveling so far for our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've really grown...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you must be tired, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My youth prevents me from tiring so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my good friend, Ran, and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're very humbled by your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ooga Mika (29)\NShinya's Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guests may be small in number, but that doesn't lead to a lonely wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm told the bride's side of the family won't even be attending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, not in front of the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:19.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ooga Tae (78)\NShinya's Grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young lady, I trust President Suzuki is doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's always playing golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look as spirited as ever, Tae-obaasama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, I have yet to find an heir to the Ooga Financial Group that will cause me no worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what gives me the energy to work as hard as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Carillon Symphonica
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran, how would Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does Shinichi already have one like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:34.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Stad House
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you just finished looking through the ornamental glass museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I just got here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, it's Tae-obaasan and Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old mistress is interested in antique glasswork.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says it's from the 17th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did glass even exist that long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In Ancient Egypt, glass was manufactured as early as 3000 BC.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was that early, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Experts claim that glass-blowing began during the Roman Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That includes glass windows as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to be quite knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I work with glass in Otaru, a town in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I requested time off from work in order to come see the glass utensils here in Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm also an admirer of glass — hence why I have a studio in the middle of this theme park.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join us for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, you can tell us about your making glass in Otaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's possible, it'd be my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:59.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Dom Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So high...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of those buildings look like toys from up here, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scenery isn't bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, I loved high places.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, seeing all those people down there bustling like ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a wonderful feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a glass artisan from Otaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invited him along in order to ask him about glassmaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ooga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:12:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is my son Shinya's wedding, which is why our entire family has gathered here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:08.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mochida Hideo (53)\NOoga Bank Vice President\NShinya's Uncle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never thought it'd be Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} that would end up marrying first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, seems he got around to it before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's only because I do not settle for less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please join us for tomorrow's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd love to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In time, Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} will become the heir of the Ooga Financial Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, attending the wedding isn't going to do you any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm simply a glass worker...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot refuse such an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wear this at the wedding tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:13:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For generations, this ring has been worn by the wife of the Ooga's first-born son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the Meiji era, the first generation of the then-merchant Ooga family...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brought this ring back from their first trip to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you rushing things a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Mother, I wore this ring at my wedding as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you passed it along to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because everyone thought of you as the perfect wife for Tatsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can always wait for the rest of the Ooga family to accept her before putting the ring on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, are you all saying Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still isn't acceptable as my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there won't be a problem with putting the ring on her finger at the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we really got invited to a high-class wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder the wedding has to be held on the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I already tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the day of a wedding, the bickering never stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is the old lady so hard on Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said that if he wasn't allowed to marry Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would leave and never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason his family agreed to the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is such a nice person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The family of a financial group has all sorts of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it because a poor girl's marrying into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That, and since she is older than him by two years, which displeased the old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fireworks show is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going over there to get a better look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At times like this, it's inconvenient to be small.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:52.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Huis ten Bosch Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, you look amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, after the wedding, be sure to toss me the bouquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I can toss it well enough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only an hour before the wedding now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's it feel looking at your bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really... lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting hot, getting hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gazing at the bride with your mouth open is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait in the lounge until the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:17:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come to act as the bride's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle stepped on the power, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it of Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just a heart palpitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be fine with a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hang onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should rest in your room before the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae-obaasama should be all right, shouldn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's nothing serious, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ring is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That ring... I-It's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a picture of Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A picture taken by Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in June when we came here to arrange the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I cannot find that ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will never be forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just a silly ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's find that ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That ruby ring went missing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That—is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cancel this wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without the ring, we'll go without a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, you're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, now, mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look around, Masayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since this wedding was brought up, we've had nothing but misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of it's the fault of that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, even our treasured family heirloom, that ruby ring, is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is not Akane's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what is she doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw her in the lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have been hit hard by all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, the wedding is about to commence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ruby ring has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one our ancestors brought back from Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That ruby ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until my sister came in with the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Shinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a strange choice of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you be implying that one of us took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and her friends came inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ring—it was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What that means is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It had to be someone who came in afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's that glass worker from Otaru, Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the ring went missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that remained was this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} should be the one who took this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only ones who could get their hands on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the members of the Ooga family, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not necessarily the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,z Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has that picture too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's also possible that she took the ring herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just so she could bring more misfortune to the Ooga family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can that be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being held under suspicion isn't comfortable for us either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, take a good look at each of our rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should the ring not be found, the wedding will be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still missing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ring that small could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and think I should go see how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what did the old lady mean by "misfortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was almost killed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's happened twice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam, the brakes won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second was on a sunny morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened while we were walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she was saved at the last minute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The missing ring today marks the third occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma Tae can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it's Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It had to be someone who came in and took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s not in the lounge!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her wedding dress was left there...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now I can't find her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could what Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said have been true?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.53,0:24:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really took the ring herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is absolutely not that kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's find her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what about the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.50,0:24:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without it, there won't be a wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.33,0:24:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking there was something strange about the hydrangea in the photo the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In flower language, they're "frivolous."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet there's some place that's connected with hydrangeas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what's going to happen to the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.56,0:24:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.44,0:24:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bride is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.19,0:24:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll split up and look for her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.65,0:24:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.74,0:24:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.78,0:24:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll look for the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.74,0:25:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hydrangea...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.33,0:25:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where should we start looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.33,0:25:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.83,0:25:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.22,0:25:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hydrangea...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.47,0:25:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Frivolous...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.30,0:25:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Frivolous...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.10,0:25:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Siebold...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.68,0:25:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.77,0:25:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard of him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.52,0:25:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Siebold was the one who brought Japanese plants to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.06,0:25:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I think one of them was...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.32,0:25:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hydrangea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.49,0:25:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scientific name for one of the hydrangea was "Hydrangea otakusa."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.87,0:25:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Siebold named it after his nickname for his Japanese wife, Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.79,0:25:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what it was, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.09,0:25:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.59,0:25:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The meaning of Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.01,0:25:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otakusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.89,0:26:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.56,0:26:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.11,0:26:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.78,0:26:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.74,0:27:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, I'm not sure who hid it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.87,0:27:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.33,0:27:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sculptures in this fountain are of Aphrodite and Psyche!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.21,0:27:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.92,0:27:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.04,0:27:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.42,0:27:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.42,0:27:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.05,0:27:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.39,0:27:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.85,0:27:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s high heels!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.93,0:27:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Women don't walk in high heels without wearing both, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.02,0:27:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means she must have been kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.98,0:27:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finding the ring was easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.61,0:27:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.78,0:27:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.99,0:27:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It likely fell to the bottom of the windmill.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.58,0:27:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.00,0:27:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.46,0:27:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.54,0:27:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was violently taken away by someone or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.71,0:28:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you implying she was kidnapped!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.30,0:28:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.88,0:28:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have run away from here ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.89,0:28:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already checked the Huis ten Bosch gates, and it doesn't seem anyone like her left.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.18,0:28:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.89,0:28:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A while ago, one of her parents planned an arranged marriage for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.56,0:28:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's still talking to that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.07,0:28:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For all we know, she may have come here just to make a fool out of Shinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.28,0:28:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would know her the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.41,0:28:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as Grandma said.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.58,0:28:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you have absolutely no idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.58,0:28:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't even know who all she dated in the past, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.88,0:28:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.96,0:28:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man she was arranged to marry was a disciple of Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.13,0:28:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something that happened ten years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.43,0:28:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he resigned and left ten years back, he was never heard from again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.64,0:28:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.77,0:28:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,( All right, let's stop talking about this for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:28:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may have mentioned it to everyone, but ultimately, there may be no wedding at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.40,0:29:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If word about the outcome of this wedding does get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.61,0:29:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reputation of the Ooga Group will be tarnished.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.49,0:29:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll have no choice but to rethink Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.13,0:29:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.71,0:29:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thin hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.71,0:29:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About this length.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.21,0:29:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she might be wearing a pink one-piece dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.01,0:29:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.30,0:29:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen her before?,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.80,0:29:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she went into the windmill house alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.31,0:29:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was this, may I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.98,0:29:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just after I came back from my lunch break...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So around 1:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.11,0:29:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 1:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.03,0:29:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this is a kidnapping as you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.70,0:29:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you're implying that the culprit is among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.66,0:29:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we can't say so with certainty...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.83,0:29:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's highly likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.50,0:29:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.04,0:29:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you even know what you' e saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.38,0:30:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, it's all right, Mochida.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.09,0:30:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, why have we all been gathered here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.26,0:30:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone saw Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at 1:00 this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An employee here that sells maps watched her enter the windmill.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.85,0:30:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, would all of you please tell us where you were at 1:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.48,0:30:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to check our alibis?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.56,0:30:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was here sorting the checkbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.65,0:30:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife and I stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.24,0:30:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 1:00, I was in the Friesland sector of the park horseback riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.45,0:30:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the marriage was on its way to being called off...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.04,0:30:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the main hall to drink some beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.25,0:30:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.54,0:30:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 1:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.33,0:30:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went back to the ornamental glass museum to look at the glasswork on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.71,0:30:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.96,0:30:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.80,0:30:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.72,0:30:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want any of the pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.26,0:30:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can get a print-out for you at the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.85,0:30:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.52,0:30:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.10,0:31:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Mochida, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.35,0:31:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.40,0:31:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything worth noting about Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s family?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.53,0:31:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father is famous in Nagasaki for the glasswork store he owned.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.24,0:31:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.03,0:31:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.24,0:31:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People say he committed suicide after being unable to pay back the loan he owed Ooga Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.79,0:31:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, our elder madam owns that glass shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.09,0:31:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he had offered its mortgage to the bank as a collateral guarantee, she could get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.55,0:31:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she wanted his shop so badly, she reduced the repayment window for his loan and took it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.43,0:31:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many people criticized her for it, but they were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.48,0:31:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were only doing honest business.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.40,0:31:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.94,0:31:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've seen this man before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.07,0:31:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was sitting and drinking beer alone over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.24,0:31:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.12,0:31:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I remember this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.29,0:32:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seemed to really take to this place and even went up to the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.29,0:32:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.54,0:32:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.09,0:32:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.09,0:32:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta go a little further back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.72,0:32:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is—the place where the minute hand's pointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.43,0:32:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's 3:05...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.01,0:32:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means that, when he took the picture, it wasn't 1:00 but instead 2:05!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.81,0:32:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the face of the clock isn't numbered...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.10,0:32:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People would mistake the time as 1:00 just by the angle of the hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.48,0:32:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assuming that person kidnapped Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the windmill around 1:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.66,0:32:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And didn't come here until 2:05...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.53,0:32:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} shouldn't be too far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.16,0:32:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably being held somewhere between the windmill house and the flower clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.12,0:32:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to find her as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.63,0:32:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you say you prefer high places, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.17,0:32:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.55,0:32:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are we going to go on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.89,0:32:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.06,0:33:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.39,0:33:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.82,0:33:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does the melody sound so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.82,0:33:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.86,0:33:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bells aren't chiming!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.45,0:33:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want to get on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.62,0:33:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.92,0:33:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.00,0:33:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it gives me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.92,0:33:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.75,0:33:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet you're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.20,0:34:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.50,0:34:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} put Tae-obaasama...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.75,0:34:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.05,0:34:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.09,0:34:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Tae-obaasan right now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.01,0:34:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.18,0:34:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.97,0:34:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She got on a hot air balloon with Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just then.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.51,0:34:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.26,0:34:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hot air balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.85,0:34:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's turning into a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.42,0:34:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.05,0:35:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.89,0:35:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.89,0:35:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.10,0:35:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.12,0:35:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.54,0:35:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.21,0:35:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That device is set to detonate a bomb on the hot air balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.55,0:35:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.17,0:35:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.72,0:35:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.31,0:35:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ended up saving me from danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.98,0:35:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.48,0:35:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.44,0:35:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.94,0:35:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.74,0:36:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.74,0:36:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.87,0:36:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you know him from somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.33,0:36:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.91,0:36:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why on earth was Grandma put in such a dangerous situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.63,0:36:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.35,0:36:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.77,0:36:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.94,0:36:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.44,0:36:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This series of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.40,0:36:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was originally orchestrated by two apathetic individuals, but because it all happened at once, by{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.78,0:36:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed like the work of a single perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.83,0:36:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.25,0:36:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae-obaasama.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.54,0:36:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.75,0:36:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.83,0:37:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who first opposed the wedding between Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.22,0:37:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.22,0:37:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just a heart palpitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.80,0:37:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be fine with a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.14,0:37:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.31,0:37:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.02,0:37:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.77,0:37:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, give it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.48,0:37:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.15,0:37:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.32,0:37:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.99,0:37:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.78,0:37:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.91,0:37:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.37,0:37:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a fountain in Central Square, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.29,0:37:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was found around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.21,0:37:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the ring had been hidden nearby, someone may have come across it during our search.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae-obaasama told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.46,0:37:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you hid it at the fountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.80,0:37:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.09,0:37:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.97,0:37:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could the picture of the hydrangea flowers possibly mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.89,0:37:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was deceived by the picture as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.31,0:37:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, because it said "frivolous" in flower language...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.06,0:37:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought the picture was attempting to relay that Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been unfaithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.31,0:38:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that picture—it has another meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.11,0:38:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.69,0:38:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water in that fountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.78,0:38:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flows like a waterfall, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.41,0:38:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.62,0:38:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the more minor hydrangea flowers was named "Hydrangea otakusa."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.08,0:38:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This name was assigned by Siebold.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Otakusa" was his nickname for his wife, Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.79,0:38:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O{\b1}ta{\b0}kusa, O{\b1}taki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, "{\b1}Taki{\b0}" ({\b1}waterfall{\b0}), see?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.42,0:38:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.30,0:38:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You already knew, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.22,0:38:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.55,0:38:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the picture at first seemed to be telling us something was wrong with Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.01,0:38:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really just telling us the secret location of the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.02,0:38:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the culprits responsible for hiding the ring are...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.40,0:38:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma and Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.82,0:38:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s kidnapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.65,0:38:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a total coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.90,0:38:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} felt responsible for losing the ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.33,0:38:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thought about running away from her wedding to Shinya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.62,0:38:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She left on her own from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.33,0:39:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you tell us what happened next...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.33,0:39:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.09,0:39:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I left the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.80,0:39:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to see Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.43,0:39:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And decided to quietly follow him...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.73,0:39:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.69,0:39:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.90,0:39:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I intend to teach that old woman a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.86,0:39:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.16,0:39:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.78,0:39:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the reason your father's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.50,0:39:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the person who stole your ring is the one named "Mika."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.96,0:39:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.96,0:39:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was the old woman that masterminded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.54,0:39:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.54,0:39:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.88,0:39:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.84,0:39:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I was rescued by Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.76,0:39:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was being held in the Carillon Symphonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.05,0:39:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, the person who mentioned Grandma earlier is Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s previous fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.98,0:40:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for hiding it from you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.06,0:40:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, when I saw Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.19,0:40:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.11,0:40:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd been ten years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.86,0:40:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you met with Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.37,0:40:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I asked him why he came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.70,0:40:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that his reason for coming was just to see the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.71,0:40:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.67,0:40:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure if that was the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.71,0:40:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, open your eyes and witness what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.01,0:40:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long do you plan on laying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.55,0:40:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.43,0:40:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.93,0:40:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because even though you claimed you were from Otaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.31,0:40:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you saw Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wedding dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.81,0:40:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were speaking the Nagasaki dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.82,0:40:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My, so pretty."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.73,0:40:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who sabotaged the brakes in Grandma's car...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.07,0:40:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one who pushed the rock from above...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.24,0:40:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.20,0:40:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.70,0:40:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because my master...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.83,0:40:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akane's father, was...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.49,0:41:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Driven to death by this old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.87,0:41:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, because of Ooga Bank's sudden demand for the loan repayment...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.21,0:41:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Felt he had nowhere else to go, and committed suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.30,0:41:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That painful expression on my master's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.51,0:41:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.13,0:41:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.43,0:41:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.89,0:41:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you be so down on yourself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.81,0:41:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leaving Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} behind like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.44,0:41:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All because some old woman wanted to use his glass factory to indulge in some hobby of hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.23,0:41:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prior to that incident, orders from several major clients had been decreasing significantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.11,0:41:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Master and I went to ask one of our wholesalers...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.53,0:41:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He admitted he had no choice, saying that Ooga Bank had pressured him to reduce his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.41,0:41:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.00,0:41:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.75,0:41:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother loved Katori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s glasswork...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.71,0:41:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So of course she hoped he would continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.34,0:41:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got to a point where she wanted to help him run his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.01,0:42:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Katori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pride as an artisan would never allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.43,0:42:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'When it comes to my glass, I will only sell to those who appreciate its worth."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.44,0:42:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that principle, the only glass products he produced were elaborate ornaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.15,0:42:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the prices were extremely high...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.65,0:42:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they were high-quality pieces of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.61,0:42:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The operation costs weren't profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.99,0:42:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that his debts had continued to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.91,0:42:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.70,0:42:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We gave him an extra day to pay us back...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.50,0:42:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then two days became a week, and one week became two.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.79,0:42:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were only a small bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.96,0:42:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We couldn't drag it on for...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.09,0:42:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.17,0:42:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.13,0:42:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying, Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.06,0:42:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.39,0:42:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master was never that weak of a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.31,0:42:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always woke up early, to pour blood, sweat, and tears into his work from dawn until dusk...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.52,0:42:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His hands would teach a novice like me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.82,0:42:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason Grandma opposed the marriage to Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.74,0:43:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because of the rash decision she'd made in the past that indirectly caused her father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.91,0:43:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why she couldn't bring herself to face Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.71,0:43:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And because of this, Akane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came to know Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} planned to avenge her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.01,0:43:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she had to be locked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know what he has done is unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.09,0:43:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, please, could you forgive Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.31,0:43:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.60,0:43:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.73,0:43:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.23,0:43:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.23,0:43:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.65,0:43:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you were to play the bride's father, Mochida...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.19,0:43:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, despite being young, how about we let Takahashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do it instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.78,0:43:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.95,0:43:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I approve!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.62,0:43:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.16,0:43:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.08,0:43:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you allowing them to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.45,0:43:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that the ring's here, I couldn't disapprove even if I wanted, could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.08,0:43:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.08,0:43:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma intended to do this from the beginning, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.84,0:44:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the ring was found, the two people could marry one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.43,0:44:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.93,0:44:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sculptures on that fountain are of Aphrodite and Psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.39,0:44:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aphrodite was jealous of her own son, Cupid, for falling in love with Psyche...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.73,0:44:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she set up a series of trials to test Psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.52,0:44:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in the end, Psyche passed every test, and earned Aphrodite's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.74,0:44:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fountain depicts that final scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.91,0:44:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma had her hide the ring there...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.33,0:44:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only because she had heard of the Greek myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.29,0:44:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the picture of the hydrangea, she tried to hint at the connection between Siebold and "taki."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.50,0:44:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.71,0:44:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's those horizontally-written foreign symbols—who knows what they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.05,0:44:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.72,0:44:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just blame everything on me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.43,0:45:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.73,0:45:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you vow to love one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.69,0:45:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.72,0:46:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should've been me getting ready to marry Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.69,0:46:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.52,0:46:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.23,0:46:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fate just isn't on my side.
